# Webapp Guidance

- Follow `webapp/STYLE_GUIDE.md` for canonical style, accessibility, and testing standards.
- Prefer shared components from `@mattermost/shared` over hand-rolled equivalents.
- Use `Button` from `@mattermost/shared/components/button` for text-based button UI instead of building bespoke `<button>` elements or styling.
- Use `WithTooltip` from `@mattermost/shared/components/tooltip` for tooltips instead of wiring up Floating UI or other tooltip primitives directly.
- Always import shared components via the full package name (`@mattermost/shared/...`), never via relative paths into `platform/shared/`.
